
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Consultant acknowledgement email</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Poppins' , sans-serif; font-size:14px;color:#302c2b; line-height:2;">
    <div class="rt-tb-scrl">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>Dear Sir / Madam,</p>
            <p>This is with reference to the consultant engagement request received for <b>@Model.PersonName</b>, from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate</b> to <b>@Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the Project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the retainer fee of <b>Rs. @Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
            <p>The following will be the next steps from our end.</p>
            <p>
                <ol type="1">
                    <li>Commitment booking</li>
                    <li>Dean IC&SR approval</li>
                    <li>Order Release</li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>For any queries please email to <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in </a> and we will get back to you at the earliest.</p>
            <p>Thanks and Regards,</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0px;">
                @Model.DAName<br>
                Project Recruitment<br>
                Centre for IC&SR<br>
                IIT Madras<br>
                *This is a system generated email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
